#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/members_join.md:1
msgid "Joining a Training Event"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/members_join.md:3
msgid ""
"When a site signs a new member contract or otherwise schedules a training"
" event with the Carpentries, the Program Manager will contact the site to"
" discuss instructor training.  This includes reviewing the training "
"curriculum and certification process."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/members_join.md:5
msgid ""
"The Program Manager will share the member training process and the "
"current member training calendar with the member site, and the site can "
"choose the dates that work best for them."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/members_join.md:7
msgid ""
"The Program Manager will share information about the training with all "
"participants, including a link to our application form and some pre-"
"reading material."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/members_join.md:9
msgid "Host Checklist"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/members_join.md:11
msgid ""
"Our training events are typically offered using the Zoom "
"videoconferencing platform."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/members_join.md:13
msgid ""
"Before the event, the Workshop Administration Team will be in touch with "
"the host site to set a test run of the Zoom videoconferencing set up. For"
" the test run, the host should:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/members_join.md:15
msgid "be in the same room as the event itself"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/members_join.md:16
msgid ""
"use the same equipment (computer, projector, speakers, microphone) as the"
" event itself"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/members_join.md:17
msgid "make sure people in the room can see and hear the person on the screen"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/members_join.md:18
msgid "make sure the person on the screen can see and hear all participants"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/members_join.md:20
msgid "Other things to be set up for the event include:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/members_join.md:21
msgid ""
"Reminding participants of the pre-reading material that was shared by the"
" Program Manager"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/members_join.md:22
msgid ""
"Reviewing the schedule to arrange for lunch and coffee breaks. Providing "
"refreshments is suggested (people learn better with fuel!), but not "
"mandatory.  A sample schedule is here."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/members_join.md:23
msgid ""
"Allowing for break out space during the event. The training includes "
"partner and small group activities. If the room is big enough this can be"
" done in different corners of the room.  Otherwise, a hallway alcove or "
"nearby office may be a good fit."
msgstr ""

